summary: I usually think that my fiancé is more like Dan and I'm more like Phil. Then I remember when he bought a really big box of...
body: I usually think that my fiancé is more like Dan and I’m more like Phil. Then I remember when he bought a really big box of cereal that was meant to be just for me since I’m funny with breakfast foods, and I only got two bowls because he ate the rest of it. The betrayal still hurts.
